# Site reference

Use the curated slices in `~/Projects/convmem/docs/site-reference/` before
promoting changes across environments or writing to production.

## Read this when

- comparing test results across practice, preview, staging2, or prod
- after sync scripts (`sync-staging2-to-practice.sh`, `sync-practice-to-preview.sh`)
- before git push to `willowyhollow-dev` staging or any production write

## Slices (pre-promote order)

1. `docs/site-reference/site-address-consistency.md` — `siteurl` / `home` match this env
2. `docs/site-reference/php-version-parity.md` — major.minor matches test and target
3. `docs/site-reference/backup-before-write-gate.md` — fresh verified backup before prod

Application guide: `docs/site-reference/NOTES.md`

Any gate failure is **blocking**. Session loop: `docs/WILLOWYHOLLOW-SESSION-LOOP.md` step 4b.
